帕马语族属于[[帕瑪-努干語系|帕瑪-努干語系]]，主要分布在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[昆士兰州|昆士兰州]]的[[约克角半岛|约克角半岛]]，最早由语言学家{{le|肯尼斯·黑尔|Kenneth L. Hale}}提出。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Classification of Northern Paman Languages, Cape York Peninsula, Australia; A Research Report|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_oceanic-linguistics_winter-1964_3_2/page/248|last=Hale|first=Kenneth L.|authorlink=Kenneth L. Hale|journal=Oceanic Linguistics|publisher=Oceanic Linguistics, Vol. 3, No. 2|issue=2|doi=10.2307/3622881|year=1964|volume=3|pages=248–265|jstor=3622881}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Paman group of the Pama–Nyungan phylic family. Appendix to Languages of the World: Indo-Pacific Fascicle Six, by G.N. O'Grady, C. F. & F.M. Voegelin|last=Hale|first=Kenneth L.|authorlink=Kenneth L. Hale|journal=Anthropological Linguistics|issue=2|year=1966|volume=8|pages=162–197}}</ref> 

== 分类 ==
帕马语族能够被细分为以下几个语支：
<ref name="Dixon">See Dixon (2002), pp. xxx–xlii.</ref>

顺着东海岸分别为：
* '''[[北约克角帕马语支|北约克角帕马语支]]''' (Northern Paman and Umpila)
* [[乌姆宾德哈姆语支|乌姆宾德哈姆语支]] （Umbindhamu） (†)
* '''[[拉马拉米克语支|拉马拉米克语支]](Lamalamic)''': Umbuygamu (†), Lama-Lama (几近绝迹) (密切关联)
* [[雅尔加拉瓦语支|雅尔加拉瓦语支]] (Yalgawarra) (分布于[[弗林德斯岛|弗林德斯岛]]) (†)
* '''[[雅兰吉克语支|雅兰吉克语支]](Yalanjic)''': Guugu Yimidhirr, Gugu Yalandyi, Barrow Point (†)
* [[姆拉里曼-古丁马语支|姆拉里曼-古丁马语支]](Mbariman-Gudhinma) (Gugu Warra) (内陆) (†)
* [[迪亚布加逸语支|迪亚布加逸语支]](Djabugay) (†)
顺着西海岸分别为：
* '''北约克角帕马语支 (Northern Paman and Umpila) '''
* '''[[西南帕马语支|西南帕马语支]] (Southwestern)''' (See)Gurdjar language
* [[科克纳尔语支|科克纳尔语支]] (Kok Narr) (†)
* '''[[诺尔曼-帕马语支|诺尔曼-帕马语支]]（Norman Paman）''': {{le|葛地爾語|Gurdjar language}}、{{le|丘森特語|Kuthant language}}（密切相關）
* [[古加迪语支|古加迪语支]](Gugadj) (†)
在内陆还有：
* {{Anchor|Gugu Mini}}'''Thaypan''' (Rarmul Pama, closely related): Thaypan (?Rarmul) (nearly extinct), Aghu Tharrnggala (†), Ikarranggali–Alungul–Angkula (†), Takalak (†)
* '''Southern''': Agwamin (†), Mbabaram (†), Mbara (†), Walangama (†)

